query:
INSERT INTO
                eth_txs_history (
                    eth_tx_id,
                    base_fee_per_gas,
                    priority_fee_per_gas,
                    tx_hash,
                    signed_raw_tx,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at,
                    blob_base_fee_per_gas,
                    sent_at_block,
                    sent_at
                )
            VALUES
                ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, NOW(), NOW(), $6, $7, NOW()) ON CONFLICT (tx_hash) DO NOTHING
            RETURNING
                id
